# Final Closeout

```
IRON LAW: NO SHIP WITHOUT FRESH, INDEPENDENT CLOSEOUT VERIFICATION
```

Violating the letter of this rule is violating the spirit of this rule.

## Purpose
Final verification refresh before ship approval, ensuring nothing is stale.
Mitigates: stale final verification before governed ship decision.

